<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Home</title>

    <style>
        body.home {
            color: var(--ink);
        }

        .page {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 12%, rgba(240, 97, 58, 0.12) 0%, transparent 45%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 0%, rgba(31, 138, 112, 0.15) 0%, transparent 45%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 1240px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 28px 16px 70px;
        }

        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 0.8fr);
            gap: 24px;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 32px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .eyebrow {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.22em;
            color: var(--muted);
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        .lead {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .btn.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(240, 97, 58, 0.24);
        }

        .btn.primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .btn.ghost {
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            color: var(--ink);
            background: #fffaf4;
        }

        .hero-metrics {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .metric {
            background: #fffaf4;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
        }

        .metric strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .metric span {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .hero-card {
            background: #fffaf4;
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .checklist {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 10px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .checklist li {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent);
            margin-top: 6px;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }

        .section {
            margin-top: 32px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }

        .section p {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .feature-grid,
        .courses-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .feature-card,
        .course-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(27, 20, 15, 0.08);
        }

        .feature-card h3,
        .course-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .course-card p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .cta-band {
            margin-top: 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(240, 97, 58, 0.15), rgba(31, 138, 112, 0.12));
            border: 1px solid var(--line);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 22px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .cta-band h3 {
            margin: 0 0 6px;
            font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(12px);
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: var(--delay, 0s);
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .hero {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="home">

    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <main class="page">
        <div class="container">
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="reveal" style="--delay: 0s;">
                    <p class="eyebrow">E-Learning Platform</p>
                    <h1>Learn skills that move your career forward.</h1>
                    <p class="lead">Curated courses, guided practice, and clear milestones designed for real progress.</p>

                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a class="btn primary" href="/register">Start learning</a>
                        <a class="btn ghost" href="/courses">Browse courses</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-metrics">
                        <div class="metric">
                            <strong>120+</strong>
                            <span>Lessons</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric">
                            <strong>32</strong>
                            <span>Practice sprints</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="metric">
                            <strong>4.9</strong>
                            <span>Average rating</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-card reveal" style="--delay: 0.1s;">
                    <div class="card-title">This week plan</div>
                    <ul class="checklist">
                        <li><span class="dot"></span>Complete the JavaScript Essentials module</li>
                        <li><span class="dot"></span>Review the weekly recap and notes</li>
                        <li><span class="dot"></span>Submit the mini project by Sunday</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Next milestone:</strong>
                        <div>Mini project submission on Sunday</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="section reveal" style="--delay: 0.15s;">
                <h2>Why learners choose us</h2>
                <p>Simple structure, clear outcomes, and a steady learning rhythm.</p>
                <div class="feature-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Guided paths</h3>
                        <p>Step-by-step lessons with checkpoints and practical tasks.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Mentor notes</h3>
                        <p>Weekly review notes and feedback to keep you on track.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Career focus</h3>
                        <p>Build a portfolio with projects that match real roles.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="section reveal" style="--delay: 0.2s;">
                <h2>Explore courses</h2>
                <p>Short lessons built to help you learn faster with less noise.</p>
                <div class="courses-grid">
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>HTML & CSS</h3>
                        <p>Build clean, responsive layouts from scratch.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>JavaScript Essentials</h3>
                        <p>Learn variables, functions, DOM, and async flow.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>Node.js & Express</h3>
                        <p>Create fast APIs and server-side apps.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>MongoDB Basics</h3>
                        <p>Design schemas and query data efficiently.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>React Fundamentals</h3>
                        <p>Build reusable UI with components and hooks.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>Python for Beginners</h3>
                        <p>Start coding with syntax, loops, and functions.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>Data Structures</h3>
                        <p>Learn arrays, stacks, queues, and linked lists.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>UI/UX Basics</h3>
                        <p>Design clean interfaces and improve usability.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-card">
                        <h3>Git & GitHub</h3>
                        <p>Version control, branching, and collaboration.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="cta-band reveal" style="--delay: 0.25s;">
                <div>
                    <h3>Ready to start learning?</h3>
                    <p class="lead">Create your account and track progress from day one.</p>
                </div>
                <a class="btn primary" href="/register">Get started</a>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
